snippet.title: Wanderlust: Rebirth Trailer
snippet.description:
Wanderlust: Rebirth is an online 4 player co-op retro arcade-action RPG. Wanderlust: Rebirth offers more content than most professionally-funded games including story and survival modes, online high-scores, over 40 enemies types, 15 boss battles (including 4 secret bosses), over 50 unique skills between 4 uniquely crafted character classes, AND MUCH MUCH MORE! 

Try it here: www.wanderlustgame.com
